78e7a2eb-6d3e-4e68-b3c0-5b2826ec32aa.name: Env
78e7a2eb-6d3e-4e68-b3c0-5b2826ec32aa.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT JSONExtractString(labels, 'env') AS env
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4
WHERE metric_name = 'go_memstats_alloc_bytes_total'
  AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'env') != '';

9996084e-0dba-4bd1-802d-5c79ed477c0a.name: Service Name
9996084e-0dba-4bd1-802d-5c79ed477c0a.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name') AS service_name
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4
WHERE metric_name = 'go_memstats_alloc_bytes_total'
  AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name') != '';
